23:20.734 --> 23:22.778
<i>She saved her thanks
for the creatures</i>

23:22.944 --> 23:24.780
<i>she had been told of as a child</i>

23:24.946 --> 23:26.823
<i>whose influence,
she was certain,</i>

23:26.990 --> 23:29.785
<i>extended as far as London.</i>

24:08.615 --> 24:12.410
<i>Unfortunately, the more abundant
the blessings,</i>

24:12.577 --> 24:14.621
<i>the more we forget to pray.</i>

24:46.069 --> 24:48.822
<i>"You are charged with
