Plenty of flanges do well
with just one.

26:20.205 --> 26:22.582
And what of you, miss?
You take an eye?

26:22.749 --> 26:26.211
- Lace.
- Not too dear.

26:26.378 --> 26:28.213
Reason to hope
on transportation, then.

26:28.380 --> 26:31.258
I'm past that hope.
I had my opportunity.

26:31.424 --> 26:36.263
Doesn't seem right,
just giving you the one.

26:36.429 --> 26:39.140
Well, the world
don't operate on right.

26:39.307 --> 26:41.142
That it doesn't.

26:41.309 --> 26:43.603
To hell with them
and their gallows.

26:43.770 --> 26:46.189
Give them a good, long piss
as you dangle.

26:46.356 --> 26:48.525
Make a mess for them
to mop after.

26:48.692 --> 26:50.735
So long as you don't go easy.

26:51.945 --> 26:55.156
So, you sailed
the boat prior, then?

26:55.323 --> 26:56.783
Made it far as Carolina.

26:56.950 --> 26:59.369
Musha! The Americas!

26:59.536 --> 27:01.204
How was it?

27:01.371 --> 27:03.415
I don't know,
I didn't stay long enough

27:03.581 --> 27:05.500
