before heading back to London.

27:05.667 --> 27:07.544
I didn't give it a chance.

27:07.711 --> 27:10.130
Shame.
I hear there's chances there.

27:10.297 --> 27:12.173
You could try a bribe.

27:12.340 --> 27:14.551
Warden would free his own heart
from his chest

27:14.718 --> 27:16.094
for a bit of gold.

27:16.261 --> 27:18.054
Just ran out.

27:18.221 --> 27:20.181
Would I could give you
some of mine.

27:20.348 --> 27:22.142
You've got gold?

27:22.309 --> 27:24.811
Had. Quite a bit.

27:24.978 --> 27:26.646
Held it in keeping.

27:27.689 --> 27:29.065
Drank my share

27:29.232 --> 27:31.609
