41:10.177 --> 41:12.847
<i>There were good days
and there were bad</i>

41:13.013 --> 41:16.934
<i>in the usual balance,
but there were many.</i>

41:17.101 --> 41:19.728
♪ Home to you

41:20.771 --> 41:26.193
♪ How I've waited
for this moment

41:27.611 --> 41:30.114
♪ To be by your side

41:33.242 --> 41:35.536
♪ Your best friend
wrote and told me

41:35.703 --> 41:41.876
♪ You had teardrops
in your eyes... ♪

41:43.043 --> 41:44.795
<i>The farm flourished</i>

41:44.962 --> 41:46.839
<i>under the eye
of the Widow Richardson,</i>

41:47.006 --> 41:48.841
<i>as she was ever after known,</i>

41:49.008 --> 41:52.595
<i>when not Mum,
or, in time, Gran.</i>

41:52.761 --> 41:54.805
Oh, thank you, my dear.

41:57.391 --> 42:00.644
Of course, you must never
fall asleep by a stream.

42:00.811 --> 42:06.567
No, for the alp-luachra
might crawl into your mouth

42:06.734 --> 42:08.903
and make his home in your belly.

42:09.069 --> 42:13.490
