42:13.657 --> 42:15.826
so no matter how much you eat,

42:15.993 --> 42:20.164
after, you'll never be
full up, never.

42:20.331 --> 42:21.290
Never!

42:21.457 --> 42:23.417
Never. Never.

42:25.085 --> 42:26.503
Oh, oh.

42:26.670 --> 42:28.255
Mother, that's enough.

42:34.053 --> 42:37.514
<i>There seemed no room for
the spirits of old in Virginia,</i>

42:37.681 --> 42:41.393
<i>so Essie no longer
told her tales.</i>

42:42.436 --> 42:44.021
<i>She kept them in her heart,</i>

42:44.188 --> 42:46.982
<i>where they warmed her
